1 the Board but shall not exceed seventy-five dollars ($75.00). The fee for renewal of a certificate
2 of licensure for a business firm is the same as the renewal fee for a corporation.
3 (d) Refunds for Denied Licensure. – Should the Board deny the issuance of a certificate
4 of licensure to any applicant, the unobligated portion of fees paid shall be returned by the Board
